Package uk.ac.uea.mathsthing

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IFormula
    Provides the required methods for a representation of a mathematical formula.
    IFormulaLexer
    Provides methods that will allow a lexer to accept and tokenise a provided mathematical formula.
    IFormulaParser
    Provides methods to interact with the parser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constants
    Provides methods to handle mathematical constants in a provided formula.
    Formula
    A simplistic implementation of a mathematical formula representation.
    Functions
    Provides methods to handle mathematical functions in a provided formula.
    Lexer  
    SimpleParser
    A simplistic parser that converts a formula from infix notation to postfix.
    Token  
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    TokenType
    Represents a component of a formula as either an TokenType.OPERATOR, TokenType.OPERAND, TokenType.CONSTANT, or TokenType.FUNCTION.
